```{r}

citiesurl <- "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vSiB6dGOgnjEe27tNq6KEOAGKAy3FpkiLx34EU7Yp-JUrTdYXBotRNpnbgxx8pQtjE8YyIEB2FlNEfo/pub?gid=1409890218&single=true&output=csv"

# View the data

```
```{r explore-data}
# Get a summary of the data
glimpse(city_funding)

# Check for any missing values
colSums(is.na(city_funding))

# Check the date range in our data
min_funding <- min(city_funding$Year)
max_funding <- max(city_funding$Year)
cat("Data ranges from", min_funding, "to", max_funding)
summary(city_funding)

```
